created: 2020-09-30, last updated: 2026-06-12, [Read more](https://www.apideck.com/file-storage-api/folders)

# File Storage Folders API
One unified API to sync folders across all major file storage platforms.
Build once, integrate everywhere.
Get started for freeAPI Reference
## Unified Folders Operations
Standard CRUD operations normalized across all platforms
ListGET
`/folders`
Retrieve all folders with pagination and filtering
GetGET
`/folders/{id}`
Fetch a single folder by ID
CreatePOST
`/folders`
Create a new folder
UpdatePATCH
`/folders/{id}`
Update an existing folder
## Quick Start
...
```
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/node'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY',
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'user-123'
})
// List folders from any connected file storage platform
const response = await apideck.file-storage.foldersAll()
// Returns normalized data regardless of the underlying platform
console.log(response.data)
// [
// { id: '123', ...
},
// { id: '456', ...
}
// ]
// Works the same for Xero, QuickBooks, NetSuite, etc.

